App Flow and Roles: Next 9

Single User Journey: Generate and Curate Aesthetic Grid

First-Time Setup

(No setup required. User is directed immediately to the main generation screen.)

Core Flow

User uploads a Style Reference Image (PNG or JPG) into the input panel.

The System analyzes the image to determine the core aesthetic (the "Vibe") and displays the "Generate My Next 9" button.

User clicks the "Generate My Next 9" button.

The System generates 9 new images and displays them in the 3x3 grid.

User clicks on one or more images to select/keep them, then uploads a new reference image for fresh inspiration, and clicks "Generate My Next 9" again to fill the empty spots.

What's NOT Included

No login/authentication.

No ability to export or share the entire grid as a single image.

No multi-user roles or permissions.
